01:49:05,088 --> 01:49:06,673
Decorated army veteran.

1286
01:49:07,174 --> 01:49:09,676
Present for the liberation of Dakau.

1287
01:49:10,594 --> 01:49:12,346
Former U.S. marshal.

1288
01:49:12,513 --> 01:49:13,597
Known proclivity for violence.

1289
01:49:13,680 --> 01:49:15,516
Shows no remorse for his crime
because he denies

1290
