1347
01:52:11,400 --> 01:52:12,943
Do you understand?

1348
01:52:16,905 --> 01:52:18,240
Yeah, I understand.

1349
01:52:19,116 --> 01:52:21,160
I understand just fine.

1350
01:52:22,327 --> 01:52:26,415
If... if I don't play along
with your little game here.

1351
01:52:26,415 --> 01:52:29,168
Dr. Naehring is gonna turn me into
