01:52:29,168 --> 01:52:30,794
What about my partner?

1353
01:52:31,462 --> 01:52:35,924
You're gonna tell the U.S. marshal's office
that he's a defense mechanism?

1354
01:52:37,843 --> 01:52:39,136
Hello, boss.

1355
01:52:57,279 --> 01:53:00,824
What the fuck is going on here?

1356
01:53:03,869 --> 01:53:05,537
You working for him?

1357
01:53:05,954 --> 01:53:11,335
I'm sorry. There wasn't any other way.
Someone had to stick with you. Keep you safe.

1358
01:53:13,295 --> 01:53:15,255
You've been watching me, huh?

1359
01:53:15,923 --> 01:53:17,883
Watching me every minute.

1360
01:53:19,677 --> 01:53:21,095
Who... who are you?

1361
01:53:21,470 --> 01:53:22,846
Who are you?
Tell me.

1362
01:53:23,347 --> 01:53:25,182
Don't you recognize me, Andrew?

1363
01:53:26,975 --> 01:53:29,687
I've been you primary psychiatrist
for the last two years.

1364
01:53:30,938 --> 01:53:32,439
I am Lester Sheehan.

1365
01:53:38,654 --> 01:53:41,281
And I told you about my wife ...

1366
01:53:41,365 --> 01:53:44,618
- I know.
- I climbed down a cliff to get you.

1367
01:53:44,868 --> 01:53:49,415
I trusted you. I risked everything
to come in here after you. Everything!

1368
01:53:49,415 --> 01:53:50,541
I know, boss.

1369
01:53:50,541 --> 01:53:52,292
We're running out of time here, Andrew,

1370
01:53:53,669 --> 01:53:56,296
I swore before the board of
overseers that I could construct

1371
01:53:56,296 --> 01:53:58,924
the most radical, cutting edge role-play

1372
01:53:58,924 --> 01:54:01,552
ever attempted in psychiatry and
it would bring you back.

1373
01:54:01,552 --> 01:54:04,221
I thought if we let you play this out

1374
01:54:04,888 --> 01:54:08,017
we could get you to see how
untrue, how impossible it is.

1375
01:54:09,351 --> 01:54:11,061
You've had to run of the place for two days.

1376
01:54:11,729 --> 01:54:14,690
Tell me, where are the Nazi experiments?

1377
01:54:15,524 --> 01:54:17,359
The satanic O.R.'s?

1378
01:54:30,539 --> 01:54:32,291
Andrew, listen to me.

1379
01:54:34,668 --> 01:54:36,337
If we fail with you

1380
01:54:37,504 --> 01:54:39,923
then everything we've tried
to do here will be discredited.

1381
01:54:39,923 --> 01:54:41,133
Everything.

1382
01:54:43,510 --> 01:54:45,846
We are on the front line of a war here, old boy.

1383
01:54:47,348 --> 01:54:49,850
And right now, it'll come down to you.

1384
01:54:56,732 --> 01:54:58,901
Don't move! Don't move!

1385
01:54:58,901 --> 01:55:02,154
- Andrew, no!
- My name is Edward Daniels.

1386
01:55:02,988 --> 01:55:05,908
This one is loaded.
I can tell by the weight.

1387
01:55:05,908 --> 01:55:08,077
I see. And that's your firearm marshal?
You're sure?

1388
01:55:08,535 --> 01:55:10,162
My initials are on the side and there's a dent in the
barrel from when Philip Stacks shot at me.

1389
01:55:10,162 --> 01:55:14,500
You're not going to fuck with my mind on this
one Doc

1390
01:55:14,500 --> 01:55:17,711
Then blast away, because that's the
only way you're ever getting off this island.

1391
01:55:24,468 --> 01:55:26,011
Andrew, please don't.

1392
01:55:37,147 --> 01:55:38,232
My gun...

1393
01:55:45,364 --> 01:55:47,032
What have you done to
my Goddamn gun.

1394
01:55:48,075 --> 01:55:49,702
It's a toy, Andrew.

1395
01:55:52,454 --> 01:55:54,123
We're telling you the truth.

1396
01:55:55,582 --> 01:55:59,086
Dolores was insane. Manic-depressive.
Suicidal.

1397
01:55:59,420 --> 01:56:02,673
You drank. Stayed away.
Ignored what everyone had told you.

1398
01:56:02,673 --> 01:56:05,801
You moved to that lake house after
she, purposely,

1399
01:56:05,801 --> 01:56:08,554
set your city apartment on fire

