01:57:14,870 --> 01:57:16,872
I told you not to come in here.

1417
01:57:17,414 --> 01:57:18,791
I told you...

1418
01:57:19,625 --> 01:57:22,086
this would be the end of you.

1419
01:57:42,523 --> 01:57:43,440
I'm back.

1420
01:57:44,775 --> 01:57:48,904
We got him just outside of Oklahoma.
Must of stopped ten places

1421
01:57:48,946 --> 01:57:50,948
