I could sleep for a week.

1422
01:57:55,995 --> 01:57:56,829
Dolores?

1423
01:58:03,919 --> 01:58:05,754
Dolores?

1424
01:58:12,761 --> 01:58:13,721
Dolores?

1425
01:58:28,235 --> 01:58:29,111
Dolores?

1426
01:58:54,428 --> 01:58:55,721
Baby...

