02:03:57,565 --> 02:04:00,860
Rachel!
Rachel, Rachel...

1461
02:04:02,820 --> 02:04:03,904
Rachel.

1462
02:04:06,324 --> 02:04:07,992
Rachel who?

1463
02:04:11,704 --> 02:04:12,788
Rachel Laeddis...

1464
02:04:14,415 --> 02:04:15,624
My daughter.

1465
02:04:19,503 --> 02:04:21,172
